OL,3,C'Devoted' great grandfather dies after
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FThe family of a great-grandfather who
OL,7,Fdied in a collision in North Tyneside
OL,8,Fsay he will be "dearly missed" by
OL,9,Fthose who knew him.
OL,11,FRidley Potts suffered serious injuries
OL,12,Fin the crash on Hartley Lane, known
OL,13,Flocally as the Beehive Road, near
OL,14,FEarsdon on the morning of Tuesday 27
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FIt was reported that a Honda Jazz and
OL,18,Fa Nissan Micra had been involved in
OL,19,Fthe collision, close to the Beehive
OL,20,Fpub.
