OL,3,C'Devoted' great grandfather dies after
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FRidley, who was from Low Fell, was
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital where he later died
OL,8,Fon Friday 30 August.
OL,10,FIn a tribute, his family said: "Ridley
OL,11,Fwas a devoted dad, father in law,
OL,12,Fgrandad and great grandad and a good
OL,13,Ffriend to many.
OL,15,F"He was a retired painter and
OL,16,Fdecorating business owner who spent
OL,17,Fmuch of his time involved with the
OL,18,FFelling Male Voice Choir, of which he
OL,19,Fwas a long serving member.
