OL,6,F"Ridley will be dearly missed by all
OL,7,Fof his loving family and friends."
OL,9,FThe 83-year-old driver of the Honda
OL,10,FJazz car also suffered serious
OL,11,Finjuries in the collision and remains
OL,12,Fin hospital in a stable condition.
OL,14,FInvestigations into the crash are
OL,15,Fcontinuing and officers are appealing
OL,16,Ffor any witnesses to get in touch.
OL,18,FThey are particularly keen to speak to
OL,19,Fanyone with dashcam footage or CCTV
OL,20,Fpictures which could help their
OL,21,Fenquiries.
