OL,6,FSergeant John Sanderson, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police's Serious
OL,8,FCollisions Investigation Unit, said:
OL,9,F"All of our thoughts remain with
OL,10,FRidley's loved ones following this
OL,11,Ftragic incident.
OL,13,F"We will continue to support them in
OL,14,Fany way they can as they attempt to
OL,15,Fprocess their devastating loss."
OL,17,FSgt Sanderson added: "Our
OL,18,Finvestigation remains ongoing, and we
OL,19,Fare determined to establish the full
OL,20,Fcircumstances surrounding this
OL,21,Fcollision.
